Like what?

00:43.600 --> 00:45.000
Build a dam.

00:45.520 --> 00:46.360
Taxidermy.

00:48.080 --> 00:49.120
Make yoghurt.

00:52.560 --> 00:54.000
<i>♪ You know that I'm sorry ♪</i>

00:54.200 --> 00:55.800
My dad's gonna love you.

00:55.880 --> 00:57.120
<i>♪ I made you blue ♪</i>

