01:16.720 --> 01:18.680
<i>♪ Keep on running ♪</i>

01:20.200 --> 01:22.200
<i>♪ Keep on hiding ♪</i>

01:23.600 --> 01:26.480
<i>♪ One fine day,</i>
<i>I'm gonna be the one ♪</i>

01:26.560 --> 01:28.920
<i>♪ To make you understand ♪</i>

01:29.000 --> 01:31.760
<i>♪ Oh, yeah! I'm gonna be your man ♪</i>

01:31.840 --> 01:33.120
<i> At first, it was OK.</i>

01:33.640 --> 01:34.760
<i>It was a good song.</i>

01:43.120 --> 01:45.280
<i> But its appeal</i>
<i>eventually palled.</i>

01:53.400 --> 01:55.320
Do you feel bad about we did?

01:57.240 --> 01:58.400
About the man?

01:58.920 --> 02:02.280
<i> I was pleased Alyssa used "we"</i>
<i>in relation to the incident.</i>

02:02.360 --> 02:03.600
He was attacking you.

02:05.080 --> 02:05.960
Yeah.

02:06.800 --> 02:08.680
