I'd give us fucking medals or something.

02:18.880 --> 02:20.080
They probably will.

02:22.440 --> 02:23.440
<i> They didn’t.</i>

02:47.480 --> 02:50.440
<i> As the hours passed,</i>
<i>I realized that I felt different.</i>

02:51.440 --> 02:52.560
<i>Sort of new.</i>

02:55.080 --> 02:56.280
<i>She'd come back for me.</i>

02:57.200 --> 03:00.400
<i>And we were really doing something,</i>
<i>going somewhere.</i>

03:00.920 --> 03:02.280
<i>And it felt good.</i>

03:05.320 --> 03:06.960
Oh, shit.

03:09.400 --> 03:10.240
Alyssa?

