03:31.560 --> 03:32.640
-Yes.
-Don't lie.

03:33.760 --> 03:34.600
No.

03:35.120 --> 03:36.080
Well...

03:36.360 --> 03:39.360
if you get cancer, you'll only have
yourself to blame, won't you?

03:51.680 --> 03:52.800
OK.

03:52.880 --> 03:55.920
