for pump number seven.

06:41.440 --> 06:42.360
Frodo!

06:45.560 --> 06:46.400
Cash or card?

06:50.400 --> 06:51.960
Like to buy a key ring? For cancer.

06:53.000 --> 06:54.600
-Not now!

06:55.880 --> 06:56.960
Cash or card?

06:57.480 --> 06:58.680
-No.

06:59.200 --> 07:01.240
-We don't have one.

07:01.320 --> 07:02.240
Yeah, we do.

07:02.320 --> 07:04.440
-Shut up!

07:05.920 --> 07:07.560
Do you want me to call the police?

07:08.520 --> 07:10.520
They might like to know
where you got your car from.

07:11.280 --> 07:12.440
I need a toilet!

07:13.440 --> 07:15.280
Get off me!

07:15.360 --> 07:16.480
-Ah!
-Frodo, call the police.

07:24.600 --> 07:26.440
I take it you recognize that.

07:26.520 --> 07:28.200
I gave it him for his birthday.

07:29.320 --> 07:30.400
Which birthday was this?

07:30.960 --> 07:31.880
His thirteenth.

07:32.520 --> 07:36.880
I’m sorry, why on earth would you
give a 13

07:36.960 --> 07:38.120
Well, he asked for it.

07:39.400 --> 07:41.640
Actually, no,
he asked for a machete.

07:42.040 --> 07:43.400
But I said that was a bit full on.

07:45.800 --> 07:48.480
This knife has been confirmed
as a murder weapon.

07:49.360 --> 07:50.200
What?

07:50.720 --> 07:52.920
Look, James...

07:53.000 --> 07:55.720
He’s weird, OK? But he's...

07:56.640 --> 07:58.080
he’s not dangerous.

08:00.120 --> 08:03.160
You let her go, or I'll blow
your fucking head off.

08:03.240 --> 08:04.320
He's really not.

08:09.400 --> 08:11.040
-No.

08:11.960 --> 08:14.520
Come on, I'm interested.
My husband owns a couple.

08:14.600 --> 08:17.040
Ow!

08:18.440 --> 08:21.760
