15:04.160 --> 15:06.360
<i> What's happened, Alyssa?</i>
<i>Where are you?</i>

15:06.600 --> 15:08.400
<i></i>
-No.

15:10.160 --> 15:11.640
<i>Come home, Alyssa.</i>

15:13.040 --> 15:14.920
Tell Tony I said, "Fuck off."

15:24.280 --> 15:25.280
Let's go.

15:31.280 --> 15:32.680
Who was on the phone?

15:34.320 --> 15:35.280
My mum.

