16:35.400 --> 16:36.880
Cheers.

16:37.520 --> 16:38.400
Cheers.

16:42.120 --> 16:43.240
It’s really nice to meet you.

16:44.280 --> 16:45.480
Hiya.

16:46.040 --> 16:47.480
-Eunice, what--
-Come back to work.

16:47.560 --> 16:49.520
-I’m sorry--
-You have to see this.

16:49.600 --> 16:52.440
-DC Noon. You have to see this.

16:55.920 --> 16:58.280
-Seriously, Eunice, can you just--

16:58.360 --> 17:00.520
-For fuck's sake!
-You have to see this.

17:00.600 --> 17:02.120
-No!
-You have to. It's important.

17:02.200 --> 17:04.319
-Not now.
-Yes, now.

17:09.000 --> 17:10.000
I'm really sorry.

17:24.360 --> 17:25.200
<i> Hey!</i>

17:25.520 --> 17:27.640
<i>I said stay still!</i>

17:27.720 --> 17:28.720
Fucking hell.

17:37.840 --> 17:39.320
Right. Let's do this.

17:41.480 --> 17:43.040
-Course I am.

17:43.120 --> 17:46.160
James, we killed a rapist,
turned our backs on the law,

17:46.240 --> 17:49.480
and I'm finally gonna meet my dad again.
It's mega. Come on.

18:14.800 --> 18:15.640
Yeah?

18:15.720 --> 18:16.800
Hi. Is Leslie in?

18:18.080 --> 18:19.360
