18:19.440 --> 18:20.600
<i> No.</i>

18:20.840 --> 18:21.680
What?

18:22.760 --> 18:23.640
Who are you?

18:27.600 --> 18:28.880
Do you know where he is now?

18:28.960 --> 18:30.720
Just leave it, James.

18:32.440 --> 18:33.280
Yeah.

18:34.160 --> 18:35.560
They still killed him.

18:37.240 --> 18:38.880
